ABOUT US
Located in the heart of Miami’s attractive Brickell neighborhood, Rosario is a tropical-chic bar where the city’s favorite Latino parties take place. Our beats and refreshing cocktails are the perfect combination for an unforgettable night out, for guests to release stress after work, or to simply enjoy a beautiful sunset with their favorite drink.
We’ve got the perfect place to make any gathering memorable and special.
